msgstr "Whether to make sure to also get world space attribute dependencies."

#: cymel.core.cyobjects.plug_c.Plug_c.affectedAttrs:12 of
msgid ""
"デフォルトの False だと、 例えば :mayanode:`transform` ノードの translate が影響を与えるアトリビュートとして "
"matrix は得られるが worldMatrix は得ることができない。"
msgstr ""
"If the default is False, for example, you can get matrix as an attribute "
"affected by the :mayanode:`transform` node's translate, but you cannot get "
"worldMatrix."

