msgstr "Index of the child you want to get"

#: cymel.core.cyobjects.plug_c.Plug_c.childNames:3 of
msgid "ロング名で得るかどうか。"
msgstr "Whether you get it with a long name or not."

#: cymel.core.cyobjects.plug_c.Plug_c.connectedElement:3
